  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/d7d4d1a15e876a3d3bde27c6f15c4933.webp?t=1759329587\" width=501 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play a chaotic action packed version of Pool where each player has a cue ball and you no longer have to wait for your turn. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/07ae6a211c20d0c155e05af8ca542421.poster.avif?t=1759329587\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/07ae6a211c20d0c155e05af8ca542421.webm?t=1759329587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/07ae6a211c20d0c155e05af8ca542421.mp4?t=1759329587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/d9ae7c436679ddf741313ac61cff224c.webp?t=1759329587\" width=500 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play on 10 different Pool tables, each unique with their own set of challenges. (With more tables to come!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/9c06223ed79746ac9891519954fc7451.poster.avif?t=1759329587\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/9c06223ed79746ac9891519954fc7451.webm?t=1759329587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/9c06223ed79746ac9891519954fc7451.mp4?t=1759329587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/d6dc4cf96a7a2acc477d86b290cb297f.webp?t=1759329587\" width=500 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left stick to aim and one button to shoot, anyone can pick-up the controller, hop on and play. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/eee65abcf01217371b147f9e74e217b8.poster.avif?t=1759329587\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/eee65abcf01217371b147f9e74e217b8.webm?t=1759329587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/eee65abcf01217371b147f9e74e217b8.mp4?t=1759329587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t have enough gamepad controllers? We got you covered! You can enjoy Pool 2 with up to 4 players on the same keyboard. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/f009aa91db2f4cb4329ccda90629c3ad.poster.avif?t=1759329587\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/f009aa91db2f4cb4329ccda90629c3ad.webm?t=1759329587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/f009aa91db2f4cb4329ccda90629c3ad.mp4?t=1759329587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/38dc69633f1f0e87e8e802c6eecc22cf.webp?t=1759329587\" width=500 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw your pool party online or in person! A perfect game to play over Discord or when chilling with your mates!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/3ffc3f1d03c86f8484f51c4cdd010d37.webp?t=1759329587\" width=500 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each game is over within 2 to 3 minutes, ensuring the fun never overstays its welcome. Players can easily drop in and out, making this the perfect game for a party! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/6011bdfed623f2bfe5756182e2dc7de5.webp?t=1759329587\" width=500 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t let simple controls deceive you. You will need a quick wit and precise aim to defeat your friends and become <strong>the ultimate Pool 2 champion</strong>.  </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/d7d4d1a15e876a3d3bde27c6f15c4933.webp?t=1759329587\" width=501 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play a chaotic action packed version of Pool where each player has a cue ball and you no longer have to wait for your turn. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/07ae6a211c20d0c155e05af8ca542421.poster.avif?t=1759329587\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/07ae6a211c20d0c155e05af8ca542421.webm?t=1759329587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/07ae6a211c20d0c155e05af8ca542421.mp4?t=1759329587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/d9ae7c436679ddf741313ac61cff224c.webp?t=1759329587\" width=500 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play on 10 different Pool tables, each unique with their own set of challenges. (With more tables to come!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/9c06223ed79746ac9891519954fc7451.poster.avif?t=1759329587\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601390/extras/9c06223ed79746ac9891519954fc7451.webm?t=1759329587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steam